Currently seeking employment: Yes, please.

I can offer you tranquility and quality, thanks to the fact that I have studied this profession as a professional, and I have immersed myself in it for many years and I like it. 🔸

Let me introduce myself, I am Duván Andrade, a Professional in Systems and Computing Engineering with 9 years of dedication in the sector since I started at the National University of Colombia in 2015. I am an extremely detail-oriented programmer, writing code that is well-commented, free of redundancy, elegant, tested, following patterns, and efficient. Every day, I continue to study to push my skills even further.

If you want me on your team, I will give my best to grow the value proposition of your company and in return, I hope for dignified conditions and challenges in which I can grow as a professional accompanied by your guiding hand.

profile_positions.description:
In this freelance job, I proposed a solution for the evolution of Colors Editores S.A.S
(30 years in the lithography and graphic arts sector), which initially managed
everything on paper and Excel, and had no digital presence. Over 2 years of work, I
delivered an attractive website, with an established online presence and SEM
campaign with Google ADS configured, and an ERP management system made with Laravel that
transitioned them from paper and Excel to efficient cloud-based work orders.
